# ── AI coding agents: per-developer local state, caches, and secret-bearing config ──
# Shared rules/context files live at the repo ROOT (AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, QWEN.md,
# .goosehints, …) and are intentionally NOT ignored. These dirs are machine-local.
# (gitignore has no inline comments — keep each note on its own line.)
.claude/
# Cursor editor + cursor-agent CLI; also holds rules — un-ignore to share them
.cursor/
.gemini/
# Qwen Code (QWEN.md at root is shared, not ignored)
.qwen/
# Augment Code (auggie)
.augment/
.goose/
# Crush local session state
.crush/
# OpenCode local state (opencode.json is shareable and NOT ignored)
.opencode/
.serena/
# Aider chat/input history + tags cache (.aider.chat.history.md, .aider.tags.cache.*, …)
.aider*

# Plumb workspace marker (commit if you want to share context with your team)
.plumb/

# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
